The purpose of this trial is to assess the efficacy and safety of E7777 (improved purity ONTAK) in patients with persistent and recurrent cutaneous T-cell lymphoma.

 A lead-in dose-finding part will be used to determine the dose of E7777 that should be used to test efficacy and safety.

